description:
Men's Fitness USA - July 2013
English | HQ PDF | 172 pages | 107 MB




Men's Fitness is for men who want to get 
more out of their lives and celebrates an upbeat, optimistic, 
pro-active lifestyle. Men's Fitness recognizes that mental 
and emotional fitness is vital to balanced living and aims 
to offer active and aspirational men - entertainment, information 
and inspiration. Providing expert workout plans and nutritional 
advice Men's Fitness is the one stop shop for anybody looking 
to lead a healthy balanced lifestyle.
